Introduction

Saay is a South Korean singer-songwriter and model. She is a former member of the girl group EvoL.

She made her solo debut on July 28, 2017 with the digital single "Circle".

On August 10, she debuted as the leader of the five-member girl group EvoL with the mini album, Let Me Explode. The group released one more album in 2013 and then went largely inactive until their official disbandment was announced in 2015.
